window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>When amateur sleuth Sabrina Daley discovers that a local hypnotherapist is giving illegal mind-altering pills to his patients, she becomes desperate to uncover his true intentions. Unfortunately, before she has the chance to confront him, the hypnotherapist is found dead.</p> <p>But who murdered him? Was it one of his patients? His bitter spouse? His assistant? Or is something more nefarious going on in Sabrina's once-idyllic small town of Treasure Cove?</p> <p>Audiobooks in The Daley Buzz Cozy Mystery Series include:</p> <ul> <li>Book 1 <i>Chocolate with a Side of Murder</i></li> <li>Book 2 <i>Caramels with a Side of Murder</i></li> <li>Book 3 <i>Apple Pie with a Side of Murder</i></li> <li>Book 4 <i>Lemon Bars with a Side of Murder</i></li> <li>Book 5<i> Cookies with a Side of Murder</i></li> </ul>"; 
